		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.she.com/?p=533444</guid>
		<description><![CDATA[ViuTV開拍新劇《i.Swim》由魏浚笙、呂爵安、邱士縉等出演，電影導演馮志強執導。周一（23日）舉行開鏡儀 [&#8230;]]]></description>

			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<div id="segment-area"><segment>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-533477 post-image" src="https://cfcdn.she.com/media/she.com/2021/08/255307-255307-Screenshot-2021-08-24-at-12.44.17-PM.png" alt="ViuTV新劇《i.Swim》開拍！Jeffery首次擔正 Edan Stanley齊齊劇中騷肌" width="480" height="546" /></p>
<p>ViuTV開拍新劇《i.Swim》由魏浚笙、呂爵安、邱士縉等出演，電影導演馮志強執導。周一（23日）舉行開鏡儀式，一眾演員齊集以校服look亮相。當然不少得首次擔正做主角的廣告寵兒、港版「臉蛋天才」魏浚笙（Jeffrey）！劇中飾演Miss翁的吳海昕（Sofiee）大爆Jeffrey操練三個月，練出四嚿腹肌！Jeffrey表示Stanley（邱士縉）@MIRROR才是「大隻排行榜」冠軍，而自己只是排第二，十分謙虛！</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-533479 post-image" src="https://cfcdn.she.com/media/she.com/2021/08/305307-305307-Screenshot-2021-08-24-at-3.52.30-PM.png" alt="ViuTV新劇《i.Swim》開拍！Jeffery首次擔正 Edan Stanley齊齊劇中騷肌" width="600" height="484" /><br />
<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-533478 post-image" src="https://cfcdn.she.com/media/she.com/2021/08/285307-285307-Screenshot-2021-08-24-at-3.52.12-PM.png" alt="ViuTV新劇《i.Swim》開拍！Jeffery首次擔正 Edan Stanley齊齊劇中騷肌" width="584" height="474" /></p>
<p>被指是「大隻排行榜」冠軍的Stanley卻表示要減肌，怕太大隻飾演學生會很奇怪。Stanley在《大叔的愛》演技水準獲網民大讚，之後演藝作品接不停手，早前的《IT狗》才剛煞科，就有新劇拍！他表示對於是否擔正做主角無所謂，只要角色有挑戰性、有戲做已經好開心。同樣拍攝《大叔的愛》的Edan（呂爵安）@MIRROR表示自己出演《大叔的愛》後知道自己的不足的地方，希望在這次中繼續進步，展示另一面的Edan予大眾。Edan又指因為要在新劇中騷肌，因此密密操練大隻，令一眾粉絲超期待他的表現！</p>
<p><blockquote class='instagram-media' data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink='https://www.instagram.com/p/COuaoNfgeSG/' data-instgrm-version='8' style=' background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);'><div style='padding:8px;'> <div style=' background:#F8F8F8; line-height:0; margin-top:40px; padding:50.0% 0; text-align:center; width:100%;'> <div style=' background:url(data:image/png;base64,); display:block; height:44px; margin:0 auto -44px; position:relative; top:-22px; width:44px;'></div></div> <p style=' margin:8px 0 0 0; padding:0 4px;'> <a href='https://www.instagram.com/p/COuaoNfgeSG/' style=' color:#000; font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:14px; font-style:normal; font-weight:normal; line-height:17px; text-decoration:none; word-wrap:break-word;' target='_blank'></a></p> <p style=' color:#c9c8cd; font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:14px; line-height:17px; margin-bottom:0; margin-top:8px; overflow:hidden; padding:8px 0 7px; text-align:center; text-overflow:ellipsis; white-space:nowrap;'>A post shared by <a href='' style=' color:#c9c8cd; font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:14px; font-style:normal; font-weight:normal; line-height:17px;' target='_blank'></a> (@) on <time style=' font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:14px; line-height:17px;' datetime=''></time></p></div></blockquote> <script async defer src='//www.instagram.com/embed.js'></script></p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-large wp-image-533445 post-image" src="https://cfcdn.she.com/media/she.com/2021/08/524904-524904-IMG_0187-819x1024.jpg" alt="Edan密密操練大隻" width="819" height="1024" /></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">劇中還有首度拍劇的ANSONBEAN（陳毅燊）、「翻版柯震東」王智騫（Martin）和Alton（王智德）@MIRROR。ANSONBEAN指他在劇中的角色較有自信，並會與Stanley有火花四濺的對手戲，令人十分期待！Martin早前到內地拍戲，表示在港拍攝用母語更親切，又指自己運動天份不高，劇中有許多動作都要比別人更多時間練習，需要MIRROR的肌肉擔當Alton教導動作。</span></p>
<p><blockquote class='instagram-media' data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink='https://www.instagram.com/p/CS6wBOvFlR0/' data-instgrm-version='8' style=' background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);'><div style='padding:8px;'> <div style=' background:#F8F8F8; line-height:0; margin-top:40px; padding:50.0% 0; text-align:center; width:100%;'> <div style=' background:url(data:image/png;base64,); display:block; height:44px; margin:0 auto -44px; position:relative; top:-22px; width:44px;'></div></div> <p style=' margin:8px 0 0 0; padding:0 4px;'> <a href='https://www.instagram.com/p/CS6wBOvFlR0/' style=' color:#000; font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:14px; font-style:normal; font-weight:normal; line-height:17px; text-decoration:none; word-wrap:break-word;' target='_blank'></a></p> <p style=' color:#c9c8cd; font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:14px; line-height:17px; margin-bottom:0; margin-top:8px; overflow:hidden; padding:8px 0 7px; text-align:center; text-overflow:ellipsis; white-space:nowrap;'>A post shared by <a href='' style=' color:#c9c8cd; font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:14px; font-style:normal; font-weight:normal; line-height:17px;' target='_blank'></a> (@) on <time style=' font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:14px; line-height:17px;' datetime=''></time></p></div></blockquote> <script async defer src='//www.instagram.com/embed.js'></script></p>
<p></p>
